      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically flawless, the high-pressure VANOS system has been fully overhauled, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure long-term structural rigidity. Power is delivered through a precise six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, riding on factory-spec suspension with zero bushing deflection. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with no signs of oxidation or road rash. A true analog masterpiece for the discerning collector.",
